findings.title: Owner can delist tokens
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to delist tokens when they have not renounced ownership.

findings.title: Owner Privileges: Modification of tokenFeeCollector and listingFeeCollector
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change tokenFeeCollector and listingFeeCollector, which can lead to unauthorized modifications.

findings.title: Owner can change listingFee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the listing fee.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude tokens from fees.

findings.title: Owner can change admin
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change the admin, which may lead to unauthorized changes and potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change fee for token
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the fee associated with a token.

findings.title: Owner can change supported chains
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change supported chains.
